mengg.classes.main

Class RankInputImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • mengg.classes.main.RankInputImpl

  • public class RankInputImpl
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Prasannjit This classifies the paragraphs for an "unseen" input into positive and negative Used to rank the document collection given the list of positive and negative attributes set for the input state This is then compared to the gold-standard csv files and results are printed
